title: Natchez Trace Parkway: Photo Gallery
body: Photo Gallery       The following albums will give you an opportunity to see the Natchez Trace Parkway throughout the year. Two of the galleries (Natchez Trace images by Marc Muench, Spring and Natchez Trace images by Marc Muench, Autumn) contain images that are copyrighted by Marc Muench. For more information about Muench Photography, and to look into obtaining usage rights for these images, please e-mail Muench Photography here.                   Natchez Trace images by Marc Muench, Spring   29 Photos  In April 2010 renowned photographer Marc Muench photographed the Natchez Trace Parkway. All photos NPS/© Marc Muench. For more information about obtaining use rights for these images, please contact Muench Photography at info@muenchphotography.com          Natchez Trace images by Marc Muench, Autumn   22 Photos  Photographer Marc Muench returned to the Natchez Trace Parkway in autumn of 2010. All photos NPS/© Marc Muench. For more information about obtaining use rights for these images, please contact Muench Photography at info@muenchphotography.com          Historic Places   6 Photos  See images of historic places along the Natchez Trace Parkway.            Plants   6 Photos  Plants          Wildlife   9 Photos  Wildlife          Scenic Views   9 Photos  Enjoy views of the Natchez Trace Parkway.            Public Domain, High Resolution Images   18 Photos  This gallery contains a variety of images suitable for media use or other high-quality needs. All images in this gallery are public domain, and may be used without copyright concerns.
